video.title: Qué pobres tan ricos
video.synopsis: A millionaire family and a working-class clan who have nothing in common are forced to live together in this comedic love story.

episodes.synopsis: The Ruíz Palacios finally return to their mansion. Lupita and Don Chuy suspect that Frida is pregnant with Tizoc’s baby. Frida takes a pregnancy test.
episodes.title: Episode 138

episodes.synopsis: Alejo threatens to take away custody of Emiliano if Lupita refuses to marry him. Lupita finds out Alejo and Minerva have Miguel Ángel’s letter.
episodes.title: Episode 139

episodes.synopsis: Leo breaks up with Diego Armando. Minerva talks to Lupita hoping to dig up more dirt on Miguel Ángel. Diego Armando works things out with his father.
episodes.title: Episode 140

episodes.synopsis: Frida tells Tizoc she’s not pregnant. Lupita agrees to marry Alejo for fear of losing Emiliano. Alejo tells the board the clause has been fulfilled.
episodes.title: Episode 141

episodes.synopsis: Lupita tells Miguel Ángel she married Alejo and he wants to know how he blackmailed her into it. Tizoc tries to convince Perla to stop taking pills.
episodes.title: Episode 142

episodes.synopsis: Lupita talks to Wendy to tell her Nepo is in love with her. Ana Sofía forges Miguel Ángel’s signature. Nepo asks Wendy the big question.
episodes.title: Episode 143

episodes.synopsis: Emiliano’s attitude with his family suddenly changes. Miguel’s family finds out Alejo has fulfilled the clause and Mati won´t let him take possession.
episodes.title: Episode 144

episodes.synopsis: Doña Mati covers for Alejo but demands he annul the marriage he forced Lupita into. Alejo makes it clear to Lupita he will refuse to grant a divorce.
episodes.title: Episode 145

episodes.synopsis: Nepo tells Wendy he’s still married to Diego’s mother. Mati names Miguel Ángel company president. Mati tells Frida it’s obvious she’s pregnant.
episodes.title: Episode 146

episodes.synopsis: Wendy introduces her new friend Rita to the Menchacas. Doña Mati takes the deeds to Don Jesús to finalize the property transfer.
episodes.title: Episode 147

episodes.synopsis: The Menchacas rent a room for Rita at the Nopalera. Alejo tells Lupita he wants Emiliano to stay with him. Ana Sofía denies knowing the Menchacas.
episodes.title: Episode 148

episodes.synopsis: Lupita finds out Alejo is the one responsible for what happened at the diner. Nepo sees Rita at the Menchacas’ diner and says they’ve forgotten her.
episodes.title: Episode 149

episodes.synopsis: Doña Mati names Alejo sales manager. Wendy is determined to make Nepo and Diego Armando listen to Rita. Lupita tells Carmelita she has a breast tumor.
episodes.title: Episode 150
